JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Inventory
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause: icsw.Prod,whse, qtyonhand - qtyreservd - qtycommit as QtyAvailable,avgcost
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
icsw join
icsp on icsp.cono = icsw.cono and icsp.prod = icsw.prod
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause:
icsw.cono = {IntegrationConnector_CloudSuiteDistributionCompany} and icsp.prodtype = 'S' and icsp.statustype = 'A'
and icsw.qtyonhand - icsw.qtyreservd - icsw.qtycommit > 0

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Services
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause: codeval,descrip
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: sasta
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause: cono = {IntegrationConnector_CloudSuiteDistributionCompany} and codeiden = 'S'

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Carriers
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause: codeval,descrip
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: sasta
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause: cono = {IntegrationConnector_CloudSuiteDistributionCompany} and codeiden = 'S'

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Salesperson
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause: slsrep, name, email, slstitle, phoneno, mgr
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: smsn
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause: cono = {IntegrationConnector_CloudSuiteDistributionCompany}

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Invoice Addons
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
cast(oeeh.orderno as varchar) || '-' || lpad(cast(oeeh.ordersuf as varchar), 2, '0')  AS InvoiceNumber,
addon1.addonnet * (case oeeh.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as ShippingAndHandling,
(SELECT sum(addonnet) from addon where cono = oeeh.cono and orderno = oeeh.orderno and ordersuf = oeeh.ordersuf and ordertype = 'oe' and addonno <> 2) * (case oeeh.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as OtherCharges,
(oeeh.taxamt_1 + oeeh.taxamt_2 + oeeh.taxamt_3 + oeeh.taxamt_4) * (case oeeh.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as TaxAmount
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
oeeh 
left join addon addon1 on addon1.cono = oeeh.cono and addon1.ordertype = 'oe' and addon1.orderno = oeeh.orderno and addon1.ordersuf = oeeh.ordersuf and addon1.addonno = 2

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Invoice Header
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
cast(oeeh.orderno as varchar) || '-' || lpad(cast(oeeh.ordersuf as varchar), 2, '0')  AS InvoiceNumber,
case
when oeeh.stagecd = 4 then 'Invoiced'
when oeeh.stagecd = 5 then 'Paid'
end as status,
case
when oeeh.stagecd = 4 then 1
when oeeh.stagecd = 5 then 0
end as IsOpen,
case
when oeeh.stagecd = 4 then TotInvAmt -
(select sum(aret.amount) from aret where aret.cono = oeeh.cono and
aret.invno = oeeh.orderno and aret.invsuf = oeeh.invsuf and aret.invdt = oeeh.invoicedt and aret.statustype = 0 and aret.transcd = 11) * (case oeeh.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end)  
when oeeh.stagecd = 5 then 0
end as InvoiceBalance,
coalesce(aret.duedt,oeeh.invoicedt) as DueDate,
case oeeh.transtype
when 'SO' then 'Sales Order'
when 'BR' then 'Blanket Release'
when 'DO' then 'Direct Ship Order'
when 'CS' then 'Counter Sales Order'
when 'RM' then 'Return Material Order'
when 'ST' then 'Standing Order'
when 'QU' then 'Quote'
when 'BL' then 'Blanket Order'
when 'FO' then 'Future Order'
end as ordertype,
oeeh.enterdt as OrderDate,
oeeh.invoicedt as InvoiceDate,
CAST(oeeh.custno as int) as custno,
oeeh.custpo as custpo,
oeeh.shipto as shipto,
oeeh.termstype as termstype,
oeeh.shipviaty as shipviaty,
oeeh.slsrepout as slsrepout,
oeeh.slsrepin as slsrepin,
arsc.name as name,
arsc.addr_1 as addr1,
arsc.addr_2 as addr2,
arsc.city as city,
arsc.state as state,
arsc.zipcd as zipcd,
arsc.countrycd as countrycd,
oeeh.shiptonm as shiptonm,
oeeh.shiptoaddr_1 as shiptoaddr1,
oeeh.shiptoaddr_2 as shiptoaddr2,
oeeh.shiptocity as shiptocity,
oeeh.shiptost as shiptost,
oeeh.shiptozip as shiptozip,
oeeh.countrycd as shiptocountry,
oeeh.totlineamt * (case oeeh.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as ProductTotal,
oeeh.specdiscamt * (case oeeh.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as specdiscamt,
oeeh.totinvamt * (case oeeh.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as InvoiceTotal,
oeeh.currencyty as currencyty,
oeeh.shipdt as shipdt
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
oeeh join
arsc on arsc.cono = oeeh.cono and arsc.custno = oeeh.custno left join
aret on aret.cono = oeeh.cono and aret.custno = oeeh.custno and aret.invdt = oeeh.invoicedt and aret.invno = oeeh.orderno and aret.invsuf = oeeh.ordersuf and aret.transcd = 0

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Invoice Lines
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
cast(oeeh.orderno as varchar) || '-' || lpad(cast(oeeh.ordersuf as varchar), 2, '0') AS InvoiceNumber,
oeel.lineno as lineno,
0 as releaseno,
oeel.shipprod as shipprod,
case oeel.specnstype 
when 'n' then (oeel.proddesc || ' ' || oeel.proddesc2) 
else icsp.descrip_1 
end as descrip,
oeel.qtyord * (case oeel.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as qtyord,
oeel.stkqtyord * (case oeel.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as stkqtyord,
oeel.whse as whse,
oeel.qtyship * (case oeel.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as QtyShipped,
oeel.stkqtyship * (case oeel.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as StockQtyShipped,
oeel.price as price, 
oeel.netamt * (case oeel.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as LineTotal,
oeeh.shipdt as shipdt,
oeel.unit as unit,
CAST(oeeh.custno as int) as custno,
oeeh.shipto as shipto,
oeel.promisedt as promisedt,
oeel.statustype as statustype,
oeel.specnstype as specnstype
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
oeeh
inner join oeel on oeel.cono = oeeh.cono and oeel.orderno = oeeh.orderno and oeel.ordersuf = oeeh.ordersuf
left join icsp on icsp.cono = oeel.cono and icsp.prod = oeel.shipprod

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Shipment Package
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
cast(oeehp.orderno as varchar) || '-' || lpad(cast(oeehp.ordersuf as varchar), 2, '0')  AS Shipment,
oeehp.freightamt as freightamt, 
oeehp.pkgno as pkgno,
oeehp.shipviaty as shipviaty,
oeehp.trackerno as trackerno
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: oeehp

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Shipment Header
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
cast(oeehp.orderno as varchar) || '-' || lpad(cast(oeehp.ordersuf as varchar), 2, '0')  AS ErpOrderNumber,
cast(oeehp.orderno as varchar) || '-' || lpad(cast(oeehp.ordersuf as varchar), 2, '0')   AS Shipment,
oeehp.transdt as ShipmentDate
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: oeehp

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Warehouse
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause: whse,name,addr_1,addr_2,city,state,zipcd,phoneno
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: icsd
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause: cono = {IntegrationConnector_CloudSuiteDistributionCompany}

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Cross Sells
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
icsec.prod AS SxProd,
icsec.altprod AS RelatedProd,
'ProductRelationship' AS ListType,
'CrossSell' AS ListValue
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: icsec JOIN icsp p1 ON p1.cono = icsec.cono AND p1.prod = icsec.prod JOIN icsp p2 ON p2.cono = icsec.cono AND p2.prod = icsec.altprod
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause:
icsec.cono = {IntegrationConnector_CloudSuiteDistributionCompany} AND
icsec.rectype = 'O' AND
p1.statustype = 'A' AND p1.prodtype = 'S' AND
p2.statustype = 'A' AND p2.prodtype = 'S'

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Payment Methods
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause: codeval, descrip, getDate() as ActivateOn
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: sasta
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause:
cono = {IntegrationConnector_CloudSuiteDistributionCompany} and
codeiden = 'T'

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Product Units of Measure
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
icseu.prod as prod,
icseu.units as units,
CASE when sasta.descrip = '' THEN icseu.descrip else sasta.descrip END as descrip,
icseu.unitconv as unitconv,
case when icsp.unitsell = icseu.units
    then 1 else 0
    end as isdefault
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
icseu
inner join icsp on icseu.prod = icsp.prod and icseu.cono = icsp.cono
left join sasta on icseu.units = sasta.codeval and sasta.codeiden = 'u' and sasta.cono = icsp.cono
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause:
icsp.cono = {IntegrationConnector_CloudSuiteDistributionCompany} and 
icsp.prodtype = 'S'  and
icsp.statustype = 'A'

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Product and Catalog
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
icsp.prod as erpnumber,
icsp.descrip_1 + ' ' + icsp.descrip_2 as descrip,
icsp.descrip_1+ ' ' + icsp.descrip_2 + ' ' + icsp.prod as URLSegment,
'' as DeactivateOn,
icsp.unitstock as unitstock,
CAST(icsp.sellmult as int) as sellmult,
CASE WHEN icsp.sellmult <> 0 then 'Multiple Only' else '' END as RoundingRule,
1 as TrackInventory,
icsw.listprice as listprice,
icsw.pricetype as pricetype,
icsp.prodcat as prodcat,
icsw.prodline as prodline,
icsw.vendprod as ManufacturerItem,
icsp.weight as weight,
icsp.length as length,
icsp.width as width,
icsp.height as height
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
icsp
left join icsw on icsw.prod = icsp.prod and icsw.cono = icsp.cono and icsw.whse = '{IntegrationConnector_CloudSuiteDistributionRefreshWarehouse}'
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause:
icsp.cono = {IntegrationConnector_CloudSuiteDistributionCompany} and
icsp.prodtype = 'S' and icsp.statustype = 'A'
-- NOTE - REMOVE THIS SECTION IF YOU DO NOT WANT THE CATALOG
UNION SELECT
icsc.catalog as erpnumber,
icsc.descrip_1 + ' ' + icsc.descrip_2 as descrip,
icsc.descrip_1+ ' ' + icsc.descrip_2 + ' ' + icsc.catalog as URLSegment,
'' as DeactivateOn,
icsc.unitstock as unitstock,
0 as sellmult,
'' as RoundingRule,
0 as TrackInventory,
icsc.listprice as listprice,
icsc.pricetype as pricetype,
icsc.prodcat as prodcat,
icsc.prodline as prodline,
icsc.vendprod as ManufacturerItem,
icsc.weight as weight,
icsc.length as length,
icsc.width as width,
icsc.height as height
from icsc 
where statustype = 'A' and
not exists (select 1 from icsp where prod = catalog) and
-- NOTE: This is intentional to not inadvertently include catalog entries
icsc.catalog like '<catalog mask>'

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Order Header
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
cast(oeeh.orderno as varchar) || '-' || lpad(cast(oeeh.ordersuf as varchar), 2, '0')  AS ErpOrderNumber,
CAST(oeeh.stagecd as int) as status,
case oeeh.transtype
when 'SO' then 'Sales Order'
when 'BR' then 'Blanket Release'
when 'DO' then 'Direct Ship Order'
when 'CS' then 'Counter Sales Order'
when 'RM' then 'Return Material Order'
when 'ST' then 'Standing Order'
when 'QU' then 'Quote'
when 'BL' then 'Blanket Order'
when 'FO' then 'Future Order'
end as ordertype,
oeeh.enterdt as OrderDate,
oeeh.canceldt as canceldt,
oeeh.custpo as custpo,
CAST(oeeh.custno as int) as custno,
oeeh.shipto as shipto,
oeeh.termstype as termstype,
oeeh.shipviaty as shipviaty,
oeeh.reqshipdt as reqshipdt,
oeeh.slsrepout as slsrepout,
oeeh.slsrepin as slsrepin,
arsc.name as name,
arsc.addr_1 as addr1,
arsc.addr_2 as addr2,
arsc.addr3 as addr3,
arsc.city as city,
arsc.state as state,
arsc.zipcd as zipcd,
arsc.countrycd as countrycd,
oeeh.shiptonm as shiptonm,
oeeh.shiptoaddr_1 as shiptoaddr1,
oeeh.shiptoaddr_2 as shiptoaddr2,
oeeh.shiptoaddr3 as shiptoaddr3,
oeeh.shiptocity as shiptocity,
oeeh.shiptost as shiptost,
oeeh.shiptozip as shiptozip,
oeeh.countrycd as shiptocountry,
case oeeh.stagecd
when 0 then oeeh.totlineord * (case oeeh.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end)
when 1 then oeeh.totlineord * (case oeeh.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end)
else oeeh.totlineamt * (case oeeh.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end)
end as ProductTotal,
oeeh.specdiscamt * (case oeeh.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as specdiscamt,
case oeeh.stagecd
when 0 then oeeh.totinvord
when 1 then oeeh.totinvord 
else oeeh.totinvamt
end * (case oeeh.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as OrderTotal,
oeeh.currencyty as currencyty,
oeeh.shipdt as shipdt
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
oeeh join
arsc on arsc.cono = oeeh.cono and arsc.custno = oeeh.custno

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Order Lines
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
cast(oeeh.orderno as varchar) || '-' || lpad(cast(oeeh.ordersuf as varchar), 2, '0')  AS ErpOrderNumber,
CAST(oeeh.custno as int) as custno,
oeeh.shipto as shipto,
cast(oeel.lineno as int) as lineno,
0 as releaseno,
oeel.shipprod as shipprod,
case oeel.specnstype 
when 'n' then (oeel.proddesc || ' ' || oeel.proddesc2) 
else icsp.descrip_1
end as descrip,
oeel.qtyord * (case oeel.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as qtyord,
oeel.stkqtyord * (case oeel.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as stkqtyord,
oeel.whse as whse,
oeel.unit as unit,
case oeeh.stagecd when 0 then 0 when 1 then 0 else oeel.qtyship * (case oeel.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) end as QtyShipped,
case oeeh.stagecd when 0 then 0 when 1 then 0 else oeel.stkqtyship * (case oeel.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) end as StockQtyShipped,
oeel.price as price, 
case oeeh.stagecd when 0 then oeel.netord when 1 then oeel.netord else oeel.netamt end * (case oeel.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as LineTotal,
oeeh.shipdt as shipdt,
com.noteln_1 as noteln,
oeel.promisedt as promisedt,
oeel.statustype as statustype,
case
when oeel.qtyship < oeel.qtyord and oeel.reqshipdt <= getdate() and oeeh.stagecd = 1 then 'True'
else 'False'
end as backordered
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
oeeh
inner join oeel on oeeh.cono = oeel.cono and oeeh.orderno = oeel.orderno and oeeh.ordersuf = oeel.ordersuf
left join icsp on icsp.cono = oeel.cono and icsp.prod = oeel.shipprod
left join com on oeel.cono = com.cono and com.comtype = 'oe' and oeel.orderno = com.orderno and oeel.ordersuf = com.ordersuf and oeel.lineno = com.lineno and (com.printfl = 1 OR com.printfl2 = 1)
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause:
oeeh.cono = 1
and oeeh.orderno > {IntegrationConnector_CloudSuiteDistributionStartingOrderNumber}
and oeel.orderno >  {IntegrationConnector_CloudSuiteDistributionStartingOrderNumber}
and oeeh.transtype  not in ('BL','QU','ST','FO','BR') 
and oeeh.stagecd <> 0 and oeeh.stagecd <> 9 
and oeeh.enterdt is not null
and (oeeh.transdt > DATEADD(day, -5, getdate()) or oeel.transdt > DATEADD(day,-5,getdate()))

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Addon Amounts
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
cast(oeeh.orderno as varchar) || '-' || lpad(cast(oeeh.ordersuf as varchar), 2, '0')  AS ErpOrderNumber,
addon1.addonnet * (case oeeh.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as ShippingAndHandling,
(SELECT sum(addonnet) from addon where cono = oeeh.cono and orderno = oeeh.orderno and ordersuf = oeeh.ordersuf and ordertype = 'oe' and addonno <> 2) * (case oeeh.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as OtherCharges,
(oeeh.taxamt_1 + oeeh.taxamt_2 + oeeh.taxamt_3 + oeeh.taxamt_4) * (case oeeh.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as TaxAmount
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
oeeh 
left join addon addon1 on addon1.cono = oeeh.cono and addon1.ordertype = 'oe' and addon1.orderno = oeeh.orderno and addon1.ordersuf = oeeh.ordersuf and addon1.addonno = 2

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Refresh ShipTo
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
CAST(arsc.custno as int) as custno,
arss.shipto as shipto,
arsc.custtype as custtype,
arss.name as name,
arss.email as email,
arss.phoneno as phoneno,
arss.faxphoneno as faxphoneno,
arss.termstype as termstype,
arss.pricetype as pricetype,
arsc.currencyty as currencyty,
arss.whse as whse,
arss.slsrepout as slsrepout,
arss.slsrepin as slsrepin,
arss.addr_1 as addr1,
arss.addr_2 as addr2,
arss.addr3 as addr3,
arss.city as city,
arss.state as state,
case when arss.countrycd = '' then 'US' when arss.countrycd != '' then arss.countrycd end as countrycd,
arsc.zipcd as zipcd,     
arss.shipviaty as shipviaty,
case when arss.pdcustno = 0 then '' when arss.pdcustno != 0 then CAST(arss.pdcustno as varchar) end as pdcustno,
arsc.bankno as bankno,
arss.pricecd as pricecd,
'' as pdshipto,
arss.disccd as disccd,
arss.credlim as credlim,
arss.poreqfl as porequired,
CASE WHEN arss.statustype = 'true' then 1 else 0 end as StatusType
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
arss
inner join arsc on arsc.cono = arss.cono and arsc.custno = arss.custno
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause: arss.cono = {IntegrationConnector_CloudSuiteDistributionCompany}

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: BillTo Customers
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
CAST(arsc.custno as int) as custno,
'' as shipto,
arsc.custtype as custtype,
arsc.name as name,
arsc.email as email,
arsc.phoneno as phoneno,
arsc.faxphoneno as faxphoneno,
arsc.termstype as termstype,
arsc.pricetype  as pricetype,
arsc.currencyty as currencyty,
arsc.whse as whse,
arsc.slsrepout as slsrepout,
arsc.slsrepin as slsrepin,
addr_1 as addr1,
addr_2 as addr2,
addr3 as addr3,
arsc.city as city,
arsc.state as state,
case when arsc.countrycd = '' then 'US' when arsc.countrycd != '' then arsc.countrycd end as countrycd,
arsc.zipcd as zipcd,     
arsc.shipviaty as shipviaty,
case when arsc.pdcustno = 0 then '' when arsc.pdcustno != 0 then CAST(arsc.pdcustno as varchar) end as pdcustno,
'' as pdshipto,
arsc.bankno as bankno,
arsc.pricecd as pricecd,
arsc.disccd as disccd,
arsc.credlim as credlim,
CASE WHEN arsc.statustype = 'true' then 1 else 0 end as StatusType,
case when arsc.shipreqfl = 0 then 'true' else 'false' end  as shipreqfl,
arsc.poreqfl as porequired
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: arsc
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause: arsc.cono = {IntegrationConnector_CloudSuiteDistributionCompany}

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Customer/Product
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
icsec.custno as custno,
'' as shipto,
icsec.altprod as SxProd,
icsec.prod as CustomerProd,
icsec.unitsell as unitsell
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
icsec join
arsc on arsc.cono = icsec.cono and arsc.custno = icsec.custno join
icsp on icsp.cono = icsec.cono and icsp.prod = icsec.altprod
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause:
icsec.cono = {IntegrationConnector_CloudSuiteDistributionCompany}
and icsec.rectype = 'C'
and icsec.shipto = ''
and icsp.statustype = 'A'
and icsp.prodtype = 'S'
and arsc.statustype = 1
